{"tid":110061,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人只要較左鬧鐘個晚就會訓得唔好/失眠？","createTime":"2017-02-06T12:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T15:16:25.000Z","uid":2716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29dfb9f21cd593aeb1a4e0b89baeadc7bce26a23","tid":110061,"uid":2716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:08:32.000Z","msg":"唔知開咩台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時我都算易訓得著<br />\n但個日只要較左鬧鐘要早d起身<br />\n個晚就通常會失眠/訓下醒下咁<br />\n成日搞到第二日無精神暈下暈下<br />\n有無方法搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26258cf98158a8d8f9e09e32bef7f99d8caf6c30","tid":110061,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"咁有學術成份嘅野應該開學術台"},{"pid":"bec1eaebfe1743b9e0819ee920000cae7ca69d24","tid":110061,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:15:43.000Z","msg":"個鬧鐘較晏啲"},{"pid":"6c0578d14921ec436777c6f27148728388ed1bd7","tid":110061,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:18:35.000Z","msg":"here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n較左鬧鐘=會緊張唔夠瞓 於是逼自己儘快瞓著<br />\n越逼自己越瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacf2ac6550dc916c05f361f408cdb5b0071855f","tid":110061,"uid":66788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"較完鬧鐘 就做其他野忘記佢 (我會睇漫畫"},{"pid":"1a5ba5504776306f41f42a941c0a5e9e8f89ba29","tid":110061,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"咁平時點起身翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdb24a322ca08e5d7abea83e502065ebc5831d1","tid":110061,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁平時點起身翻工<img src=\"/assets/fa