edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直用緊一個極度依賴朋友既方法<br />\n大前提係你個fd 係自己識醒同有記性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫定個friend每朝打比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然同鬧鐘既作用一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔會訓唔著<br />\n<br />\n我自己係咁啦 唔知岩唔岩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想有個咁既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d84f9f4c479f9b417909de072b0a233cdf95514","tid":110061,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知開咩台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時我都算易訓得著<br />\n但個日只要較左鬧鐘要早d起身<br />\n個晚就通常會失眠/訓下醒下咁<br />\n成日搞到第二日無精神暈下暈下<br />\n有無方法搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁簡單<br />\n臨訓醒之前先起身較鬧鐘就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}